# Final Implementation Plan for Spotify-YouTube Music Player App

## Project Overview
Complete implementation plan for a music player app that integrates with both Spotify and YouTube services, featuring a modern glassy UI with advanced playback controls and offline capabilities.

## Technical Architecture

### 1. Core Components

#### Authentication & API Integration
- Spotify SDK authentication flow
- YouTube Data API v3 integration
- Token management and automatic refresh
- User library access and synchronization

#### Media Playback System
- ExoPlayer for high-quality audio playback
- MediaSession service for background playback
- Lock screen controls integration
- Audio focus management

#### User Interface
- Glassy, modern UI with Material Design 3
- Responsive layout for all screen sizes
- Dark/Light mode support
- Animated transitions and micro-interactions

#### Offline System
- Download management with custom path configuration
- Local caching for instant playback
- Storage space optimization
- Downloaded content synchronization

### 2. File Structure

```
app/src/main/
├── java/com/musicplayer/
│   ├── data/
│   │   ├── api/              # API service implementations
│   │   ├── repository/       # Data repositories
│   │   └── database/         # Room database components
│   ├── domain/
│   │   ├── model/            # Data models
│   │   └── usecase/            # Business logic implementations
│   ├── presentation/
│   │   ├── ui/               # Activity and Fragment classes
│   │   ├── viewmodel/         # ViewModel classes
│   │   └── adapter/          # RecyclerView adapters
│   ├── service/              # Background services
│   └── utils/                # Utility classes
└── res/                      # Resources
    ├── layout/                # XML layout files
    ├── drawable/              # Drawables and vector assets
    ├── values/               # Strings, colors, dimensions
    └── mipmap/               # App icons
```

