## Implementation Phases

### Phase 1: Project Setup (Week 1)
1. Create Android Studio project with proper structure
2. Configure required dependencies:
   - Spotify Android SDK
   - YouTube Data API v3
   - ExoPlayer for media playback
   - Room database for offline storage
3. Set up AndroidManifest.xml with required permissions

### Phase 2: Core Functionality (Week 2)
1. Implement Spotify authentication flow
2. Set up YouTube API integration
3. Create repository pattern for data access
4. Implement token management and refresh

### Phase 3: Media Playback (Week 3)
1. Set up ExoPlayer for media playback
2. Implement MediaSession service
3. Create background playback service
4. Implement lock screen controls

### Phase 4: UI/UX Implementation (Week 4)
1. Design glassy UI with Material Design 3
2. Implement main activity with playlists
3. Create player activity with full controls
4. Develop settings activity

### Phase 5: Advanced Features (Week 5)
1. Implement download management system
2. Set up local storage with Room database
3. Create cache management for instant playback
4. Implement storage space optimization

### Phase 6: Testing and Optimization (Week 6)
1. Unit testing for core functionality
2. UI testing for different screen sizes
3. Performance optimization
4. Battery usage optimization

